reviewText: Sent back because not in English

With that title, I was expecting to run the gamet of emotions while on this journey with someone or some people trapped - didn't know how or why.  Well, I won't spoil it for anyone to tell what it's about, and it just may frighten some people, just not me.  I like more realistic scenarios and this just isn't that, so I gave it an 'okay'.  Let's just say this isn't a high budget movie.
SCARY, FUNNY, WEIRD, ALL WHAT A SCARY MOVIE SHOULD BE!! I RECOMMEND THIS TO ALL THE HORROR FILM LOVERS OUT THERE.
Very scary movie thats also has a good message at the end. Glad to see good horror movies still getting made. I'd recommend it
